{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Slug (スラグ)","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Glossary/Slug","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><span class=\"seoSummary\">スラグは、通常はURLの最後にあるWebアドレスの固有の識別部分です。<br>\n MDNのコンテキストでは、\"&lt;locale&gt; / docs /\" に続くURLの部分です。</span></p>\n\n<p>親文書の下に新しい文書が作成されたときの最終的な構成要素でもあります。<br>\n たとえば、このページのスラグは&nbsp;<code>Glossary/スラグ</code>&nbsp;です。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"関連情報","title":"関連情報","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/MDN/Guidelines/Writing_style_guide#%e3%82%bf%e3%82%a4%e3%83%88%e3%83%ab%e3%81%a8%e3%82%b9%e3%83%a9%e3%82%b0%e3%81%ae%e6%b1%ba%e3%82%81%e6%96%b9\">タイトルとスラグの決め方</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"関連情報","id":"関連情報"}],"summary":"スラグは、通常はURLの最後にあるWebアドレスの固有の識別部分です。\n MDNのコンテキストでは、\"<locale> / docs /\" に続くURLの部分です。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Slug","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"Slug","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Slug","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Slug","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Slug","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/glossary/slug","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/glossary/slug/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Glossary","title":"MDN Web Docs 用語集: ウェブ関連用語の定義"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Glossary/Slug","title":"Slug (スラグ)"}],"pageTitle":"Slug (スラグ) - MDN Web Docs 用語集: ウェブ関連用語の定義 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}